passes.benefit_text:
This pass allows 1/2 price admission for up to three (3) people for&nbsp; the Discovery Museum, as well as Discovery Woods. Any people accompanying the 3 pass users will still pay the regular admission fee of $19.&nbsp;
Visitors are advised to confirm Museum's public hours by visiting www.discoveryacton.org or by calling The Museum at (978) 264-4200.&nbsp;
This pass is NOT a ticket reservation; you must purchase tickets at the Museum upon arrival. Advanced tickets reservations are no longer required.

This pass offers discounted $5 admission for up to 4 adults. Admission is free for children under age 18.
&nbsp;
Patrons must present both this library pass and their timed admission ticket for entry into the museum.
&nbsp;
For more information, including health and safety requirements, please visit the ISGM's Know Before You Go page .
